{"tid":17583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又空難] 處女航成最後一程 美女副機師魂斷九霄","createTime":"2016-12-02T01:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T02:49:45.000Z","uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ffd6cdd39226d7b2bcd1957ab2cc1885d05bec5","tid":17583,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:27:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55992980&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55992980%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161202&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ce5a8049\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D55992980%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161202&h=c6285269\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=55992980&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161202</a><br />\n<br />\n巴西甲組球會查比高恩斯包機空難，罹難者包括拉米亞航空（LaMia）29歲女副機師阿里亞斯（Sisy Arias）。她在起飛前接受訪問的片段曝光，詎料成為她的遺言。<br />\n<br />\n這是阿里亞斯首次擔任民航機副機師。她在駕駛艙向記者表示非常興奮，對能夠代表玻利維亞航空公司，接載巴西球隊，與有榮焉。<br />\n<br />\n阿里亞斯除了是機師，也是玻利維亞知名模特兒。她任記者的父親尤其悲痛，現在陰陽相隔，只希望「主能保護她」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161202/280pix/1480619468_dcf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161202%2F280pix%2F1480619468_dcf0.jpg&h=95aec63b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7b4119fd8ad6234db6625eaf5f8a3e0c408177f","tid":17583,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72fdddafe71ec1dd03fa11afaba1b72b4cff4f7e","tid":17583,"uid":33979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:03:28.000Z","msg":"女人揸車同揸飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c488c0dc5047a469e88ed7ae2332793c039ee50","tid":17583,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:16:20.000Z","msg":"原來架飛機係女人渣...."},{"pid":"efa0c81f0e7f2194c6455e573265e7a8a7a9960f","tid":17583,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:20:13.000Z","msg":"終於明白個機師點解咁大懵唔記得中途入油，原來有個女副機師相陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e979c5da333fb049c7d9c881701c1e128edbc0e7","tid":17583,"uid":1778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:21:52.000Z","msg":"依家都唔肯定邊到出處，等調查報告啦"},{"pid":"d791ee9c40bf3cced7cc6c6cf2dfd8132963f331","tid":17583,"uid":1778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家都唔肯定邊到出處，等調查報告啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e0d94cf098a9e075bb263cce37d756b455daea","tid":17583,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:49:45.000Z","msg":"副機師咋"}]}